name: Aircraft Pack: C909 (Formely known as ARJ21)
description:
Brings C909 to ACEO. Not functional without ACEOTweaks-Core and ACEOTweaks-Aircraft. This aircrafts will only spawn from airline mods which include them. 
 
 Known Issue: Cleaning Truck will still spawn at the back and do not have enough space between wing and engine to attach
